title: UV Shield Sun Heat Protector (SPF 50+ PA++++)
description:
Troxederm has one focus: to bring simple, yet functional skin care to your daily life and routine. Originally intended for surgery patients experiencing hyper-sensitive and dry skin post-op, Troxederm formulas are gentle, clean, and ideal for all skin types in need of some serious TLC.

The secret to Troxederm’s efficacy? Troxerutin, an antioxidant clinically proven to not only heal, but prevent irritation, dryness, and inflammation at the source. Troxerutin is also proven to protect against UVB-related damage and promote skin cell renewal for glowing, youthful skin.

Every Troxederm product is formulated with 100% natural and EWG 1-grade ingredients for a mild — but effective — skincare experience.
